<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>Do you require financial assistance?<br></b></font><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b><br></b>There are a number of ways that Kingsbridge are able to support you to help ensure your insurance cover is not affected.<br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Please call us on&nbsp;</span><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">01242 808740</b><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;and our team will run through your options with you.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><br>Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>You agreed to pay for your Kingsbridge business insurance policy&nbsp;<b><i>[policy number]</i></b>&nbsp;through direct debit payments.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Unfortunately, our credit providers Close Brothers Premium Finance have informed us that&nbsp;<b>the most recent attempt to take payment has been unsuccessfu</b>l.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Because of this, there are instalments due for your insurance policy.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><b>Your policy is now at risk of cancellation.</b>&nbsp;If your insurance policy is cancelled,&nbsp;<u>your business may not be covered against claims if you don't have another policy in place</u>.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><b><u>If a payment has not been made before&nbsp;<i>[proposed cancellation date]</i>, your policy will be cancelled.&nbsp;</u></b><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>To help you stay protected, please call us on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;to make a payment or discuss further.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><u>Please note, for data security reasons, do not send credit or debit card details to us via email.</u><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><i>If you have made a payment in the past 3 working days please disregard this email.</i><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>